<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.1.4">
<l>eṉkoḷva ṉuṉṉaiviṭṭeṉ ṉumvācakaṅ kaḷcolliyum</l>
<l>vaṉkaḷva ṉēṉmaṉattai valittukkaṇṇa nīr karantu</l>
<l>niṉkaṇ neruṅkavaittē yeṉatāviyai nīkkakillē</l>
<l>ṉeṉkaṇ maliṉamaṟut teṉṉaikkūvi yaruḷāykaṇṇaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Although speaking words that say “what would I hold on to, having let you go?”,</l>
<l>I cannot force the mind of me who is a hard rogue, hide the tears in [my] eyes,</l>
<l>put my soul close to your eye [and] remove [it].</l>
<l>Cutting off the dirt from my eyes graciously call me, o Kṛṣṇa.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
